OL,3,CThe #13 bn hole in the government's
OL,4,C2.6% defence target
OL,6,FThe Chancellor's and the Treasury's
OL,7,Fassertion, in its latest Spending
OL,8,FReview, that by 2027 defence spending
OL,9,Fwill "reach 2.6% of GDP" is not all it
OL,10,Fseems, to the tune of about #13
OL,11,Fbillion.
OL,13,FHere's why.
OL,15,FThe published forecasts for defence
OL,16,Fspending in the financial years 2026/7
OL,17,Fand 2027/8, of #65.5 billion and #71
OL,18,Fbillion respectively in cash terms,
OL,19,Fare 2.1% and 2.2% of the OBR's
OL,20,Fforecast of "current prices" GDP in
OL,21,Fthose years.
