OL,3,CThe #13 bn hole in the government's
OL,4,C2.6% defence target
OL,6,FThis is a long way short of the
OL,7,Fpledged 2.6%. The gap in cash terms is
OL,8,F#13 billion - which is NOT a rounding
OL,9,Ferror.
OL,11,FI should start by saying that 24 hours
OL,12,Fago I asked Treasury officials to
OL,13,Fexplain the gap. It can't be hard for
OL,14,Fthem to do so. They've gone away to
OL,15,Fthink about it.
OL,17,FSo here are a few of my thoughts about
OL,18,Fwhat is going on.
