OL,3,CThe #13 bn hole in the government's
OL,4,C2.6% defence target
OL,6,FBut defence-related intelligence
OL,7,Fcannot possibly be more than a fifth
OL,8,Fof all UK spending on Mi6, Mi5 and
OL,9,FGCHQ, because Nato is very clear that
OL,10,Fthe only intelligence spending that
OL,11,Fcounts has to be directly related to
OL,12,Fmilitary operations.
OL,14,FI am going to be generous and assume
OL,15,Fspending on military intelligence that
OL,16,Fis part of the so-called Single
OL,17,FIntelligence Account and outside of
OL,18,Fthe Ministry of Defence's (MoD) budget
OL,19,Fis just over a billion pounds.
