OL,3,CThe #13 bn hole in the government's
OL,4,C2.6% defence target
OL,6,FAs Wallace says this is double
OL,7,Fcounting, because the VAT is paid to
OL,8,Fthe Treasury. When defence secretary,
OL,9,Fhe was so infuriated that one year he
OL,10,Frefused to submit numbers to Nato.
OL,12,FSo perhaps the whole of the #10
OL,13,Fbillion gap is VAT.
