OL,3,CThe #13 bn hole in the government's
OL,4,C2.6% defence target
OL,6,FAnd maybe the reason the Treasury
OL,7,Fisn't getting back to me to confirm or
OL,8,Fdeny is that it knows neither Nato or
OL,9,FPresident Trump would be impressed
OL,10,Fthat a huge proportion of our claimed
OL,11,Fdefence spending may be around #10
OL,12,Fbillion in tax payments to... the
OL,13,FBritish government.
OL,15,FAnyway, now that I've put these
OL,16,Fnumbers in the public domain, I await
OL,17,Fwith interest clarification from the
OL,18,FTreasury of what's going on here.
